reviews.review_text:
The first...what an honor! I already have the soundboard of this as part of
my complete Cap Centre box set (thanx Archive!)
I orginally got the shows on lo-fi and am now
redoing all of them in hi-fi.  Decided to check 
this audience set and I love it.  The Cap had 
a great feeling.  Too bad they tore it down and
replaced it with a crappy strip mall.  This is 
worth the download.  It'll take you right back
to those great Cap Centre dayz.
The"SMR" project SEE 1992,2,21 'getting them all!---- A TOTAL HONOR TO HAVE BEEN IN THE MAN'S COMPANY! THE LAME DANCE, THE BLIND SEE, AND THE DEAF PAID FULL PRICE FOR TICKETS!!!!!
Miss Brent Vince and his Fisher Price piano 🙄
